sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant G as kgateway<br/>(gateway ns)
  participant NP as NetworkPolicy<br/>(llama ns)
  participant V as vLLM pod
  participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU
  participant OT as OTel collector
  participant P as Prometheus

  C->>G: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer <api-key>
  Note over G: TrafficPolicy: token-bucket rate limit<br/>60 req/min per source
  G->>NP: forward to llama-llama-8b:8000
  Note over NP: allow ingress from gateway ns only
  NP->>V: reach vLLM
  V->>V: validate --api-key
  Note over V: reject 401 if bad
  V->>V: scheduler adds to running batch<br/>(KV cache alloc)
  V->>GPU: forward pass (prefill)
  GPU-->>V: first token
  V-->>C: SSE stream start (TTFT)
  loop until EOS / max_tokens
    V->>GPU: decode step
    GPU-->>V: next token
    V-->>C: stream token
  end
  V->>OT: OTLP trace spans
  V-)P: /metrics scrape (15s)
  V->>V: request_success_total{finished_reason=stop|length|abort}
